abstract: The amazing Tyler Hinman streak ends at five.
snippet: The amazing Tyler Hinman streak ends at five.
lead_paragraph: Congratulations to Dan Feyer, the new king of crosswords. Two years ago, he won the C Division. Last year, he easily took the B. This year, he won it all, beating out Howard Barkin and Anne Erdmann on the big board.

headline.main: Dan Feyer is the New A.C.P.T. Champion
